name: NOLANewOrleansGuide
0:
”Alexa, open NOLA guide”
”recommend me a coffee shop”
”where to go for breakfast”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: nola guide
des: New Orleans NOLA Guide will recommend you places for coffee, breakfast, lunch and dinner as well as tell you about attractions, weather and some history of the city. Distance to attractions is measured from the French Quarter.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
